abstract: >
  MIESC is an automated security assessment framework for Ethereum smart contracts
  that integrates 15 specialized security tools with AI-powered correlation and
  compliance mapping. Built as a Model Context Protocol (MCP) agent, MIESC enables
  collaborative cyberdefense through inter-agent communication. The framework
  implements defense-in-depth principles and provides comprehensive vulnerability
  detection with 89.47% precision, 86.2% recall, and Cohen's Kappa of 0.847
  (validated on 5,127 contracts). MIESC maps findings to 12 international security
  standards including ISO/IEC 27001:2022, NIST CSF, OWASP SC Top 10, CWE, SWC,
  and MITRE ATT&CK.
